abstract: In a contentious exchange during the last round of Democratic debates, Ms. Harris confronted Mr. Biden about having worked with segregationists in the Senate and discussed her personal history with busing. Here’s a refresher.
snippet: In a contentious exchange during the last round of Democratic debates, Ms. Harris confronted Mr. Biden about having worked with segregationists in the Senate and discussed her personal history with busing. Here’s a refresher.
lead_paragraph: Perhaps no moment from the first Democratic debates in June was more dramatic than the tense exchange between former Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. and Senator Kamala Harris of California. The two Democrats sparred on the issues of race, segregation and school busing.

lead_paragraph: DETROIT — Wednesday’s debate was barely underway when the attacks began on former Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. and Senator Kamala Harris, and some of their Democratic rivals rarely let up.

abstract: With Joseph R. Biden Jr., Kamala Harris, and Cory Booker all onstage, candidates are likely to make direct appeals to the Democratic Party’s most loyal constituency.
snippet: With Joseph R. Biden Jr., Kamala Harris, and Cory Booker all onstage, candidates are likely to make direct appeals to the Democratic Party’s most loyal constituency.
lead_paragraph: DETROIT — While the first night of the second round of Democratic debates showed off the party’s ideological diversity, the second night will look more like the Democratic base.

abstract: HBO’s new comedy series features a cast of emerging black comedians.
snippet: HBO’s new comedy series features a cast of emerging black comedians.
lead_paragraph: HBO’s “A Black Lady Sketch Show” invites viewers into uncharted territory. The series, created by Robin Thede and co-executive produced by Issa Rae, boasts a rarity for TV: a cast, writers room and director (Dime Davis) comprised entirely of black women.
